<exercise id="fs-id2293814">
<problem id="fs-id2023719"><para id="fs-id2023720">Which type of T cell is most effective against viruses?</para>
<list id="fs-id2229536" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>Th1</item>
<item>Th2</item>
<item>cytotoxic T cells</item>
<item>regulatory T cells</item>
</list>
